members.member:

This class provides functionality to seprates fingertips form an Fourprint image
made by DERMALOG live scanner.

///  Please don't use this SDK for seperating finger tips form an image made by Flatbed scanner.

member.summary:
\author Raul Chitic \date 12. Jan. 2015
This class enables access to the fourprint segmentation properties. Actually it supports only LongA properties, therefore it throws an exception for property FS2_PR_SEGMENTATION_VERSION (String). Furthermore the properties FS2_PR_SEGMENTATION_FINGER1ONPLATE up to FS2_PR_SEGMENTATION_FINGER4ONPLATE are read only.
Use only the []-operator for getting and setting properties! e.g.: long nValue = Properties[FS2_PR_SEGMENTATION_FINGER_MIN_WIDTH]; Properties[FS2_PR_SEGMENTATION_FINGER_MIN_WIDTH] = 400;
